snippet.title: Amnesia: The Dark Descent - Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for first person survival horror game Amnesia: The Dark Descent.

Amnesia is available for Windows, Mac & Linux and will only set you back a horrific 20 USD. Check http://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/amnesia-the-dark-descent if curious what reviewers think!

http://www.amnesiagame.com
